---
title: Sweet Chili Roasted Veg Bowls over Cilantro Rice with Sweet Chili Mayo & Crispy Fried Onions
description: Falling into a rice bowl rut with the same veggie + sauce combo each week? We’ve got you covered. This version features mushrooms and sweet potato, which are roasted and then coated in a tantalizing sweet chili mayo sauce. It’s all spooned over rice and garnished with crispy fried onions for crunch. The best part? It’s ready in just 30 minutes from start to finish—now that’s what we call a winning dinner.
